				  <br>&nbsp; Select action -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>				  
				  <br>&nbsp; End turn -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Press in a Circle button in a empty square to bring that menu</font>
				  <br>&nbsp; Next unit -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 or R1 Button</font>
				  <br>&nbsp; Next enemy unit -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 or R2 Button</font>				  
