<!-- Game Cheats Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
          		  <br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			      &nbsp; Unlock Blackalley -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">On stage 29, convince Elche with Jiron twice. On stage 30, have Jiron convince Elche. On the X-Point route, have Jiron convince Elche on stage 33</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Unlock Caprico -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Do not destroy her or attack Tron with an attack other then punch on stage 28, hard mode. Keep her alive for the rest of the fight</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Unlock Elche (as a pilot) -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">On stage 29, convince Elche with Jiron twice. On stage 30, have Jiron convince Elche. On the X-Point route, have Jiron convince Elche on stage 33</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Unlock Gaven Custom Borjanon -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Do not go to Fort Severn on stage 13. On stage 17, reduce Gaven's HP to less then 20% without destroying him</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Unlock Powered up Getter Robo G -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">On the second half of stage 36, destroy the Shin Getter Robo</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Unlock Powered up Mazinger Z (Moon Route) -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">On stage 36 in the second half, move Tetsuya next to Kouji</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Unlock Powered up Mazinger Z (X-Point Route) -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">In the first half of stage 36, reduce Mazinkaiser's HP to the required amount and then move Kouji next to it</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Unlock Powered up Zeta Gundam -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">On stage 39, use Camille in the Zeta Gundam and reduce Rosamie to less then 50% HP</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Unlock Qubeley -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Convince Puru 2 with Puru and Judau on stage 9. Convince Puru 2 with Judau on stage 30</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Unlock Qubeley mk. II -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Either convince Puru 2 with Judau on stage 30 or convince her with both Puru 2 and Judau on stage 9. Do not do both</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Unlock Shin Getter Robo -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">On the second half of stage 36, do not destroy the Shin Getter Robo</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Unlock Tron -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Do not destroy her or attack Tron with an attack other then punch on stage 28, hard mode. Keep her alive for the rest of the fight</font>&nbsp;<br>
          		  <br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			      &nbsp; Infinite Money -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>80073168 967F<br>8007316A 0098</font>&nbsp;<br>
				  <br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">GAMESHARK CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			      &nbsp; Infinite energy Poseidon -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8013FFC0 270F<br>8013FD0A 270F</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Infinite energy Getter 1 -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>80140368 270F<br>801400B2 270F</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Infinite energy Dragon -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8016617F 270F<br>8013F962 270F</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Infinite energy Liger -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>80140EE2 270F<br>80141198 270F</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Infinite energy Gundam Sandrock Custom -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8014128A 270F<br>80141540 270F</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Infinite energy Qubeley MK-II -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>80141632 270F<br>801418E8 270F</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Infinite energy Daitarn 3 -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8013F8F2 270F<br>8013FBA8 270F</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Infinite energy ZZ Gundam -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>80140792 270F<br>80140A48 270F</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
